B.Db=new A.cY("What are the delivery times?","Standard delivery is within 24\u201348 hours after order confirmation. For same-day delivery, orders must be placed before 10 AM on available days.")
B.Dc=new A.cY("Do you deliver to my area?","Coverage is expanding constantly. Enter your address at checkout \u2014 the app will confirm if your area is currently served.")
B.D6=new A.cY("Can I schedule delivery for a specific date?","Scheduled delivery windows are available for select areas. If available in your region, a calendar selector will appear at checkout.")
B.FC=s([B.Db,B.Dc,B.D6],t.bw)
B.KK=new A.m6(B.n2,B.FC,"Delivery")
B.Dh=new A.cY("Are the products really organic?","Products marked with the organic badge are certified by our partner farmers. Each product page shows the farm name, certifications, and harvest practices.")
B.D8=new A.cY("What if a product is out of stock?","Stock is updated in real time. If a product runs out, it will be shown as unavailable. You can add it to your watchlist and be notified when it's back.")
B.D7=new A.cY("What do the units mean (kg, unit, bunch)?",'Each product shows its unit of measure on the detail page. For example, "1 kg" means you\'ll receive approximately 1 kilogram, and "1 bunch" means a standard bunch as picked by the farmer.')
B.Fd=s([B.Dh,B.D8,B.D7],t.bw)
