B.DH=new A.d_(983127,"MaterialIcons",null,!1)
B.Dd=new A.cY("What payment methods are accepted?","Harvest currently supports credit card, debit card, and digital wallets. Payment is processed securely at checkout.")
B.Dj=new A.cY("Is my payment information safe?","All payment data is encrypted end-to-end. We never store your full card number. Transactions are protected by industry-standard PCI DSS compliance.")
B.Di=new A.cY("How do refunds work?","Refunds for cancelled orders are processed within 3\u20135 business days back to your original payment method. For quality issues, contact us within 24 hours of delivery.")
