B.Dk=new A.cY("I forgot my password. How do I reset it?",'On the Sign In screen, tap "Forgot password?" and enter your email. You\'ll receive a reset link within a few minutes.')
B.Df=new A.cY("How do I update my delivery address?","Go to Profile \u2192 Delivery Addresses to add, edit, or remove addresses. You can also set a default address for faster checkout.")
